		 <h3 class="title_bold text-center">Helicopter Tours</h3>
                 
                  <p><strong>HELICOPTER TOUR PACKAGES</strong> <br /><br /> <strong> PRETORIA / HARTBEESPORT TOUR</strong> <br />
                     <br /> Departing from Grand Central Airport in Midrand, you fly Northbound, routing along the N1 Highway towards the sprawling developments of Pretoria East. <br />
                     <br />Coming into Pretoria CBD from the south-eastern side, you will immediately recognise the landmarks that make the South African Capital City as impressive as it is. One can see the majestic Union Buildings (constructed in 1913 and now the current office of the president); Loftus stadium; Pretoria University; the Zoo, and several other iconic and administrative buildings within the City Centre. <br />
