                  <p>Once received in VIP fashion at our offices at Grand Central Airport, you take off in style, departing along the N1 south towards the Beccluech interchange. 
                     <br /> Routing over Sandton, you will see the richest square mile in Africa. You can see quite an economic difference either side of the M1 highway; Alexander township &ndash; Madiba&rsquo;s first place of residence - to the east and the luxury of Sandton to the west. 
                     <br /> Continuing along the M1, you see Melrose Arch, Rosebank, and the impressive houses of Houghton Estate. <br />
                     <br /> <span class="hidden-xs pull-right"><img class="img-rounded" style="float: right; margin: 50px 0px 10px 10px;" title="Helicopter Tour" src="<?php echo base_url('assets/frontend/home/images/'); ?>/jozi-town-map.jpg" alt="jozi-town-map" width="180" height="128" /></span> 
